</p>
<h2 id="forcing-user-to-look-dirty">Forcing User to look Dirty? <a class="headerlink" href="user-plain-password#forcing-user-to-look-dirty" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Inside <code>setPlainPassword()</code>, do one more thing: <code>$this-&gt;password = null</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="a9d7a12702">
